{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":833,"text":"When I graduated UCLA, I moved to northern California,"},{"time":4397,"text":"and I lived in a little town called Elk"},{"time":6646,"text":"on the Mendocino coast,"},{"time":8633,"text":"and I didn't have a phone or TV, but I had U.S. mail,"},{"time":13191,"text":"and life was good back then, if you could remember it."},{"time":16926,"text":"I'd go to the general store for a cup of coffee"},{"time":19648,"text":"and a brownie, and I'd ship my film"},{"time":22334,"text":"to San Francisco, and lo and behold, two days later,"},{"time":27069,"text":"it would end up on my front door,"},{"time":28865,"text":"which was way better than having to fight the traffic"},{"time":31895,"text":"of Hollywood. (Music)"},{"time":33809,"text":"I didn't have much money,"},{"time":37797,"text":"but I had time and a sense of wonder. (Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":40724,"text":"So I started shooting time-lapse photography."},{"time":43612,"text":"It would take me a month to shoot a four-minute"},{"time":46377,"text":"roll of film, because that's all I could afford."}]},{"cues":[{"time":50959,"text":"I've been shooting time-lapse flowers continuously,"},{"time":53433,"text":"non-stop, 24 hours a day, seven days a week,"},{"time":56470,"text":"for over 30 years, and to see them move"},{"time":59253,"text":"is a dance I'll never get tired of."},{"time":63299,"text":"Their beauty immerses us with color, taste, touch."},{"time":68198,"text":"It also provides a third of the food we eat."},{"time":71381,"text":"(Music)"},{"time":73844,"text":"Beauty and seduction is nature's tools for survival,"},{"time":77989,"text":"because we protect what we fall in love with."},{"time":81100,"text":"It opens our hearts, and makes us realize"},{"time":83025,"text":"we are a part of nature and we're not separate from it."},{"time":88010,"text":"When we see ourselves in nature, it also connects us"},{"time":92094,"text":"to every one of us, because it's clear"},{"time":94318,"text":"that it's all connected in one."}]},{"cues":[{"time":97373,"text":"When people see my images, a lot of times they'll say,"},{"time":100757,"text":"\"Oh my God.\" Have you ever wondered what that meant?"},{"time":105037,"text":"The \"oh\" means it caught your attention,"},{"time":107598,"text":"makes you present, makes you mindful."},{"time":110765,"text":"The \"my\" means it connects with something deep"},{"time":113349,"text":"inside your soul."},{"time":115621,"text":"It creates a gateway for your inner voice to rise up"},{"time":118365,"text":"and be heard. And \"God\"?"},{"time":121357,"text":"God is that personal journey we all want to be on,"},{"time":124965,"text":"to be inspired, to feel like we're connected to a universe"},{"time":129640,"text":"that celebrates life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":132760,"text":"Did you know that 80 percent"},{"time":135450,"text":"of the information we receive comes through our eyes?"},{"time":139261,"text":"And if you compare light energy to musical scales,"},{"time":142363,"text":"it would only be one octave that the naked eye could see,"},{"time":145389,"text":"which is right in the middle?"},{"time":147949,"text":"And aren't we grateful for our brains that can, you know,"},{"time":150773,"text":"take this electrical impulse that comes from light energy"},{"time":153821,"text":"to create images in order for us to explore our world?"},{"time":159141,"text":"And aren't we grateful that we have hearts"},{"time":160696,"text":"that can feel these vibrations"},{"time":162942,"text":"in order for us to allow ourselves to feel the pleasure"},{"time":166534,"text":"and the beauty of nature?"},{"time":169311,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":173534,"text":"Nature's beauty is a gift that cultivates"},{"time":176604,"text":"appreciation and gratitude."},{"time":178962,"text":"(Music)"},{"time":182722,"text":"So I have a gift I want to share with you today,"},{"time":185405,"text":"a project I'm working on called Happiness Revealed,"},{"time":188786,"text":"and it'll give us a glimpse into that perspective"},{"time":191834,"text":"from the point of view of a child and an elderly man"},{"time":195432,"text":"of that world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":200088,"text":"Child: When I watch TV,"},{"time":205048,"text":"it's just some shows that you just -- that are pretend,"},{"time":210492,"text":"and when you explore, you get"},{"time":213250,"text":"more imagination than you already had,"},{"time":217858,"text":"and when you get more imagination,"},{"time":221114,"text":"it makes you want to go deeper in"},{"time":223481,"text":"so you can get more and see beautifuller things,"},{"time":226572,"text":"like the path, if it's a path, it could lead you to a beach,"},{"time":233150,"text":"or something, and it could be beautiful."},{"time":235649,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":264585,"text":"Elderly Man: You think this is just another day in your life?"},{"time":271567,"text":"It's not just another day. It's the one day that is given to you"},{"time":278097,"text":"today."},{"time":281843,"text":"It's given to you. It's a gift."},{"time":287747,"text":"It's the only gift that you have right now,"},{"time":292097,"text":"and the only appropriate response"},{"time":295001,"text":"is gratefulness."},{"time":305356,"text":"If you do nothing else but to cultivate that response"},{"time":312088,"text":"to the great gift that this unique day is,"},{"time":316704,"text":"if you learn to respond"},{"time":319521,"text":"as if it were the first day in your life"},{"time":323513,"text":"and the very last day,"},{"time":326197,"text":"then you will have spent this day very well."}]},{"cues":[{"time":334641,"text":"Begin by opening your eyes and be surprised"},{"time":338470,"text":"that you have eyes you can open,"},{"time":342297,"text":"that incredible array of colors that is constantly offered to us"},{"time":347576,"text":"for pure enjoyment."},{"time":351258,"text":"Look at the sky."},{"time":354706,"text":"We so rarely look at the sky."},{"time":358166,"text":"We so rarely note how different it is"},{"time":363337,"text":"from moment to moment, with clouds coming and going."},{"time":368433,"text":"We just think of the weather,"},{"time":371159,"text":"and even with the weather, we don't think of"},{"time":373299,"text":"all the many nuances of weather."},{"time":376522,"text":"We just think of good weather and bad weather."},{"time":380647,"text":"This day, right now, has unique weather,"},{"time":385359,"text":"maybe a kind that will never exactly"},{"time":388427,"text":"in that form come again."},{"time":391215,"text":"That formation of clouds in the sky will never be the same"},{"time":395191,"text":"as it is right now."},{"time":398405,"text":"Open your eyes. Look at that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":403670,"text":"Look at the faces of people whom you meet."},{"time":408315,"text":"Each one has an incredible story behind their face,"},{"time":415738,"text":"a story that you could never fully fathom,"},{"time":422114,"text":"not only their own story, but the story of their ancestors."},{"time":429451,"text":"We all go back so far,"},{"time":432595,"text":"and in this present moment, on this day,"},{"time":436825,"text":"all the people you meet, all that life from generations"},{"time":441989,"text":"and from so many places all over the world"},{"time":446155,"text":"flows together and meets you here"},{"time":449507,"text":"like a life-giving water, if you only open your heart and drink."},{"time":455740,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":462587,"text":"Open your heart to the incredible gifts that civilization"},{"time":467954,"text":"gives to us."},{"time":469873,"text":"You flip a switch and there is electric light."},{"time":473951,"text":"You turn a faucet and there is warm water and cold water,"},{"time":479759,"text":"and drinkable water."},{"time":481910,"text":"It's a gift that millions and millions in the world"},{"time":486421,"text":"will never experience."}]},{"cues":[{"time":489837,"text":"So these are just a few of an enormous number of gifts"},{"time":494560,"text":"to which we can open your heart."},{"time":498092,"text":"And so I wish you that you will open your heart"},{"time":501890,"text":"to all these blessings, and let them flow through you,"},{"time":508270,"text":"that everyone whom you will meet on this day"},{"time":511261,"text":"will be blessed by you,"},{"time":515283,"text":"just by your eyes,"},{"time":518760,"text":"by your smile,"},{"time":522186,"text":"by your touch,"},{"time":525622,"text":"just by your presence."},{"time":529970,"text":"Let the gratefulness overflow"},{"time":533823,"text":"into blessing all around you,"},{"time":540089,"text":"and then it will really be a good day. (Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":555553,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":556452,"text":"Louie Schwartzberg: Thank you."},{"time":559393,"text":"Thank you very much. (Applause)"}]}]}